# BharatQA Landing Page — Design Audit

> **Auditor:** Senior Product Designer · **Date:** March 12, 2026
> **Page:** [bharatqa-frontend.vercel.app](https://bharatqa-frontend.vercel.app)

---

## Executive Summary

The landing page has strong copywriting and a premium dark-mode aesthetic, but it suffers from **"template-itis"** — every section relies on emojis + text with **zero product screenshots, zero human photography, and zero evidence of the actual product.** For a service that sells *"real people testing on real phones,"* the page ironically shows none of that.

